<1> ʔušuˑyakšʔalic hidiˑsis łax̌ ʔukʷiy , yaqaˑbitik ƛułuˑʔapsuˑ duˑbey , qʷaˑqeys ʔiyax̌ tiˑkaʔaˑ , huʔax̌ ƛ̓iˑʔak ʔiyax̌ kʷičiˑyeˑʔiqaˑd .
<translation> Thank you for giving me this day , for the way you always make it good , for the way I’m here , still walking on this land .

<2> ʔušuˑyakšʔalic ʔušuˑyakšʔalic .
<translation> Thank you, thank you .


